OML | ORlib Media Library 

Installation
Edit verify.php to change username and password.
make sure xml is writeable by webserveruser (most www-data): 
chown www-data:www-data xml

Usage
Create Booknotes for your own fits. Remind yourself when do you borred a book to someone. Organize Hints like ISBN, Color or Links. 
Shortform, Content, Index and Colophone will be formated by raw BBCode style:
1. [b]TEXT[/b] => <b>TEXT</b>, All simple HTML-Tags (e.g. "i" or "u")
2. [url=TEXT1]TEXT2[/url] => <a href="TEXT1">TEXT2</a>, Textlink or URL
3. [img]TEXT[/img] => <img src="TEXT" alt="TEXT" />, Images
4. All URLs (http://domain.tld/) will be formated to clickable links

